1.1 	Update
	- HA MQTT Integration added. Code refactoring
	- Fix rainfall precision
	- Adding maximum wind speeds
	- Readme updated
	- License updated
	- Inline comments updated

1.0	Initial release
	- Supported sensors:
		- Weather Meters (wind direction, wind speed, rainfall)
		- BME280 (temperature, humidity, pressure)
		- MLX90614 (ambient temperature, object temperature)
	- Sanity checks for all sensor values
	- MQTT messaging (individual sensor values and json)
	- Configurable polling time (manual and auto)
	- Configurable mean values for wind and clouds sensors
	- Remote restart with MQTT command
	- Remote programming (OTA)

